data.content:
The root cause is that `Microsoft.AspNetCore.OpenApi` 10.0 upgraded from **OpenAPI.NET v1** to **v2**, which has several breaking changes. Here's what changed and the fixes:

### 1. `Microsoft.OpenApi.Any` removed
Types like `OpenApiString` are gone. Schema values are now `System.Text.Json.Nodes.JsonNode`.

### 2. `Schema.Nullable` removed
OpenAPI 3.1 expresses nullability via the `Type` flags enum (`JsonSchemaType`), not a separate bool.

### 3. `OpenApiSecurityScheme` + `OpenApiReference` pattern replaced
Reference wrappers like `OpenApiSecuritySchemeReference` in `Microsoft.OpenApi.Models.References` replace the manual `Reference` property approach.

### Fixed code:

```csharp
using System.Text.Json.Nodes;              // replaces Microsoft.OpenApi.Any
using Microsoft.OpenApi.Models;
using Microsoft.OpenApi.Models.References;  // new reference types

options.AddOperationTransformer((operation, context, ct) =>
{
    var param = operation.Parameters.FirstOrDefault(p => p.Name == "api-version");
    if (param is not null)
    {
        // OpenApiString → JsonValue
        param.Schema.Example = JsonValue.Create("1.0");
    }

    operation.Responses.TryAdd("401", new OpenApiResponse { Description = "Unauthorized" });

    // OpenApiSecurityScheme + OpenApiReference → OpenApiSecuritySchemeReference
    var oAuthScheme = new OpenApiSecuritySchemeReference("oauth2");
    operation.Security =
    [
        new OpenApiSecurityRequirement
        {
            Schemes = new Dictionary<OpenApiSecuritySchemeReference, IList<string>>
            {
                [oAuthScheme] = scopes
            }
        }
    ];

    return Task.CompletedTask;
});

options.AddSchemaTransformer((schema, context, ct) =>
{
    if (schema.Properties is not null)
    {
        foreach (var property in schema.Properties)
        {
            if (schema.Required?.Contains(property.Key) != true)
                // .Nullable = false → clear the Null flag from the Type enum
                property.Value.Type &= ~JsonSchemaType.Null;
        }
    }
    return Task.CompletedTask;
});
```

### Summary of changes

| .NET 9 (OpenAPI.NET v1) | .NET 10 (OpenAPI.NET v2) |
|---|---|
| `using Microsoft.OpenApi.Any` | `using System.Text.Json.Nodes` |
| `new OpenApiString("1.0")` | `JsonValue.Create("1.0")` |
| `property.Nullable = false` | `property.Type &= ~JsonSchemaType.Null` |
| `new OpenApiSecurityScheme { Reference = new OpenApiReference { Type = ..., Id = "oauth2" } }` | `new OpenApiSecuritySchemeReference("oauth2")` |
| `new() { [scheme] = scopes }` (dict initializer) | `new() { Schemes = new Dictionary<...> { [scheme] = scopes } }` |
